import React from 'react'
import { Row, Col } from 'antd'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
function Loign(){
    return(
        <Row>
            <Col span={6}></Col>
            <Col span={12}>
                <form>
                    name : 
                    <input type="text"></input>
                    password :
                    <input type="password"></input>
                    <Link>  google</Link>
                    <button>login</button>
                </form>
            </Col>
            <Col></Col>
        </Row>
    )
}
export default Loign
